 * flagged as a broken link rather than silently skipped.
 *
 * Usage:
 *   deno run --allow-read .llm/tools/check-internal-doc-links.ts --pretty
 *   deno run --allow-read .llm/tools/check-internal-doc-links.ts 
--check-orphans --pretty
 *   deno run --allow-read .llm/tools/check-internal-doc-links.ts --json
 *   deno run --allow-read .llm/tools/check-internal-doc-links.ts --root 
.llm/harness --pretty
 *
 * Exit code: 0 when no enforced violation is found, 1 otherwise. Broken links 
and
 * broken anchors are always enforced; orphans are enforced only with 
--check-orphans.
 * This is wired into `deno task docs:maintenance` alongside the skill-mirror
